The paper proposes a deep learning-based method for stage detection of diabetic retinopathy using fundus images. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging and healthcare (cs.MED) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it aims to simplify the detection step for early detection of diabetic retinopathy.
